{"tid":220252,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"摩洛哥朝早定羅馬夜晚危險啲？","createTime":"2017-04-27T21:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T16:29:47.000Z","uid":4453,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d60fb311d07cbf33178aa437bf6225cb6b15965","tid":220252,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:43:01.000Z","msg":"請問有冇巴絲去過呢兩個地方可以俾下建議我，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊會去摩洛哥，頭幾日都有朋友一齊，但走嗰陣就自己去意大利，有兩個方法可以揀。<br />\n<br />\n1.喺chefchaouen坐十幾個鐘巴士(中間要轉車) 去marrackech 瞓一晚，第二天朝早飛羅馬<br />\n<br />\n2.喺chefchaouen瞓一晚，第二天喺chefchaouen坐五個鐘巴士直達 Rabat, 夜晚飛羅馬，但夜晚11點幾先到羅馬<br />\n<br />\n你地覺得邊個會安全啲？唔該哂各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ac0ffc7bec07c1d3331ef3891f481e9f7d9ee8","tid":220252,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:43:50.000Z","msg":"摩洛哥輸4粒 仲好提"},{"pid":"1fc82979e37321751397b92da76ac1277f7f2c90","tid":220252,"uid":4453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:44:56.000Z","msg":"另外想問下去過摩洛哥嘅巴絲，當地安唔安全，一個女仔去危唔危險？ Thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38b624403b20701595969abdecb7f8323ba9912","tid":220252,"uid":13534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:45:30.000Z","msg":"羅馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2939a51c5037472607a0660d51ef07608ce8dc68","tid":220252,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羅馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n羅馬好危險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打建議option 1?"},{"pid":"c55f5cb9f94c